<L>__{interior hallway late afternoon}
<A>__{as maggie, slowly approaches the front door, the doorbell rings again. she slowly leans in and peers through the peep hole. pov: the neighbour looms large. he holds in his arms a large `something' wrapped in paper. maggie pulls her head away. beat. she looks again. pov: the neighbour bends down out of sight and then rises again, turning to leave. maggie watches him go.}
